  "description": "Fall Arrives, 2023 I keep trying to write an update for y\u0026rsquo;all who subscribe to my Substack, explaining what it is I\u0026rsquo;m doing, but the issue is, I am busy doing the things!\nSo, this is going to be a poorly-written stream-of-consciousness update. It\u0026rsquo;s about 0500, and I\u0026rsquo;ll work on it until my partners get up, and then I\u0026rsquo;ll post what I have.\nThat is, perhaps, a good starting point: longer subscribers might have noticed that sometime this year, I went from saying \u0026ldquo;my partner,\u0026rdquo; to \u0026ldquo;my partners,\u0026rdquo; and someone pointed out recently that I never really explained what changed.\n",
